PractitionerGivenNameSearchParameter

Parameter practitioner.given:string

Searches for Practitioner based on the Practitioner's given name(s) eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Practitioner?given={givenName}

ResourcePractitioner
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPractitioner
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
